<p>
The OpenGuides system is <strong>free software</strong>, written in <a
href="http://www.perl.org/">Perl</a>. It is <a
href="http://search.cpan.org/author/KAKE/OpenGuides/">available
for download</a> from <a href="http://www.cpan.org/"><acronym
title="The Comprehensive Perl Archive Network">CPAN</acronym></a>.
</p>
<h2>System requirements</h2>
<p>
To run OpenGuides, you will need a webserver capable of running Perl, and
the following Perl modules, all of which are also available from CPAN. We
recommend you use <a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/CPAN/">CPAN.pm</a> or
the newer <a
href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/CPANPLUS/">CPANPLUS.pm</a> to install
them if possible for reasons of expedience.
</p>
<ul>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/Algorithm-Diff/">Algorithm::Diff</a> 0.13</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI/">CGI</a> 2.42</li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI-Carp/">CGI::Carp</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI-Cookie/">CGI::Cookie</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI-Wiki/">CGI::Wiki</a> 0.49</li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI-Wiki-Formatter-UseMod/">CGI::Wiki::Formatter::UseMod</a> 0.09</li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI-Wiki-Plugin-Categoriser/">CGI::Wiki::Plugin::Categoriser</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI-Wiki-Plugin-GeoCache/">CGI::Wiki::Plugin::GeoCache</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI-Wiki-Plugin-Locator-UK/">CGI::Wiki::Plugin::Locator::UK</a> 0.06</li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/CGI-Wiki-Plugin-RSS-ModWiki/">CGI::Wiki::Plugin::RSS::ModWiki</a> 0.02</li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/Config-Tiny/">Config::Tiny</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/DBD-Pg/">DBD::Pg</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/Data-Dumper/">Data::Dumper</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/File-Spec/">File::Spec::Functions</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/Geography-NationalGrid/">Geography::NationalGrid</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/Module-Build/">Module::Build</a> 0.18</li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/Parse-RecDescent/">Parse::RecDescent</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/Search-InvertedIndex/">Search::InvertedIndex</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://search.cpan.org/dist/Template-Toolkit/">Template</a></li>
